00:53:34,640 --> 00:53:38,960
-I'm right here, Mum.
-I have to call Cooper.

717
00:53:41,120 --> 00:53:43,800
I have to call
and make sure that he's safe.

718
00:53:44,840 --> 00:53:48,840
I have to call him. I have to call him.
I have to call him.

719
00:53:57,360 --> 00:53:58,800
Mum?

720
00:54:02,400 --> 00:54:04,720
Mum!

721
00:54:04,800 --> 00:54:08,200
Mum! Mum! Mum! Mum!

722
00:54:26,200 --> 00:54:27,800
-What happened?
-His phone rang.

723
00:54:27,880 --> 00:54:29,400
-You didn't take it off him?
