729
00:54:53,400 --> 00:54:57,160
Then went dead. Like that.

730
00:54:58,240 --> 00:55:01,760
You said he shouted something.
What was it?

731
00:55:02,320 --> 00:55:03,320
"Mum."

732
00:55:08,200 --> 00:55:11,040
-Make a note of that.
-Yes.
